/// User add a new note -->

// browser - server --> Send the user input to the server with POST req to /new-notes

The server have the response to the req done.
The response is the Status 302 Code -> Redirect (to /new-notes)

Here the browser sends the data put in the form.

// server - browser --> Redirect to /new-note

Add the new notes to notes with push
Re render all the site of /notes with the new note.

// browser - server --> get request to render /notes
// server - browser --> fetch HTML file

// browser - server --> the HTML file request the CSS and js files
// server - browser --> fetch that files

// browser - server --> get request fetching de data that is requesting in the js file
// server - browser --> render Data.Json in browser with DOM-API method





